de.loki.metallum.entity.Band.name: Desaster
de.loki.metallum.entity.Band.info:
The split release with Impiety called "Ceremonial Necrochrist Desecration" is a bootleg.
Contrary to widespread popular belief the band name is not misspelled. It's taken from the Destruction song "Total Desaster". "Desaster" is also the German spelling of "disaster".
